quran[7{c,v,t}:
2,70,"unhon ne kaha ke ( ab ke ) perwar-digaar se phir darkhwast kijiyej ke hum ko bta day ke woh aur kis kis terhan ka ho, kyunkay bohat se bail hamein aik dosray ke mushaba maloom hotay hain, ( phir ) khuda ne chaha to hamein theek baat maloom ho jaye gi"
2,71,"moose ne kaha ke khuda farmata hai ke woh bail kaam mein laga howa nah ho, nah to zameen jootna ho aur nah khaiti ko pani deta ho. is mein kisi terhan ka daagh nah ho. kehnay lagey, ab tum ne sab baatein durust bta den. gharz ( barri mushkil se ) unhon ne is bail ko zibahkiya, aur woh aisa karne walay they nahi"
2,72,"aur jab tum ne 1 shakhs ko qatalkiya, to is mein baahum jhagrnay lagey. lekin jo baat tum chhupa rahay they, khuda is ko zahir karne wala tha"
2,73,to hum ne kaha ke is bail ka koi sa tukda maqtool ko maro. is terhan khuda mardon ko zindah karta hai aur tum ko apni ( qudrat ki ) nishanain dekhata hai taakay tum samjhoo
2,74,"phir is ke baad tumahray dil sakht ho gay. goya woh pathar hain ya un se bhi ziyada sakht. aur pathar to baze aisay hotay hain ke un mein se chashmay phoot nikaltay hain, aur baze aisay hotay hain ke phatt jatay hain, aur un mein se pani niklny lagta hai, aur baze aisay hotay hain ke khuda ke khauf se gir parte hain, aur khuda tumahray amlon se be khabar nahi"
2,75,"( momino )kiya tum umeed rakhtay ho ke yeh log tumahray ( deen ke ) qaail ho jayen ge, ( halaank ) un mein se kuch log klamِ khuda ( yani torat ) ko suntay, phir is ke samajh lainay ke baad is ko jaan boojh kar badal dete rahay hain"
2,76,"aur yeh log jab mominoun se mlitay hain to kehte hain, hum imaan le aeye hain. aur jab aapas mein aik dosray se mlitay hain to kehte hain, jo baat khuda ne tum par zahir farmai hai, woh tum un ko is liye betaye dete ho ke ( qayamat ke din ) isi ke hawalay se tumahray perwar-digaar ke samnay tum ko ilzaam den.kiya tum samajte nahi ?"
